    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid shape for its next owner! It runs like a dream and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a great, dependable car without the brand-new price tag. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
